+  loaded `AgentSpec.context_budget == 50000`.
+- `test_loader_preserves_dag_field` — V2 YAML with valid
+  `dag:` entries; assert `spec.dag` is a non-empty
+  `list[Stage]`.
+- `test_existing_v1_yaml_still_loads` — minimal V1 spec; assert
